"Unzip all the downloaded files. In the :guilabel:`Browser`, locate the "
"folder containing the boundary file  "
"``WDPA_WDOECM_Apr2022_Publicc_10744_shp-polygons.shp`` and drag-and-drop it "
"into the QGIS canvas."
